# Supabase operations

For anything involving Postgres schema, RLS, RPCs, migrations, Edge Functions, or project secrets, **prefer the Supabase CLI** (`npm run supabase -- <args>`) and/or the **Supabase MCP** tools over manual dashboard-only steps. Use the dashboard when CLI/MCP is insufficient.

After changing code under `supabase/functions/`, deploy affected functions to the linked project; do not leave fixes only local.
